# File is managed by Puppet

PermitRootLogin <%= scope.lookupvar("::ssh::permit_root_login") %>
PasswordAuthentication <%= scope.lookupvar("::ssh::password_authentication") %>
<% if scope.lookupvar("::ssh::allow_users") != "undef" -%>
AllowUsers <%= scope.lookupvar("::ssh::allow_users") %>
<% end -%>

AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
GSSAPIAuthentication no
PrintMotd no
Subsystem sftp /usr/libexec/openssh/sftp-server
UseDNS no
UsePAM yes
X11Forwarding yes
